Chart Extractor
This notebook extracts and saves:

Texts: native PDF text, OCR text, page-level text, full text
Images: rendered pages, normalized pages, embedded PDF images
Charts: chart/figure candidate crops using OpenCV
Tables: tables from PDF pages using pdfplumber
Metadata: JSON and Excel summary
Supported inputs:

PDF, JPG, JPEG, PNG, TIFF, SVG

